title: Statement by the Press Secretary on HJ Res 56 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




July 28, 2009

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on HJ Res 56




THE WHITE HOUSE   Office of the Press Secretary  ___________________________________________________________________  FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE                                            July 28, 2009  STATEMENT BY THE PRESS SECRETARY    On Tuesday, July 28, 2009, the President signed into law: H.J.Res. 56, which renews the import restrictions contained in the Burmese Freedom and Democracy Act of 2003.
